==English==

===Proper Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Wheel]] of [[Fortune]]&reg;'''

#A television [[game show]] that first aired in 1975, where the objective is to solve a mystery word puzzle by filling in the letters; the cash value of each letter is determined by spinning a large wheel containing dollar amounts and various other spaces. The series was originally devised by Merv Griffin, which runs in local editions around the world, and has an American syndicated incarnation currently hosted by Pat Sajak and Vanna White.
#A computer, video, or online game based on this television game show.


